{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299", "id": 160629749, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUxNjA2Mjk3NDk=", "number": 34299, "title": "Macro to check if a function returns a specific error", "user": {"login": "tredoe", "id": 16563, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2NTYz", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16563?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe", "html_url": "https://github.com/tredoe", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tredoe/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2016-06-16T10:33:05Z", "updated_at": "2016-06-17T14:44:38Z", "closed_at": "2016-06-17T14:44:38Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "At testing, it's also necessary to have a macro to checking a specific error returned by a function.\n\nThis macro gets it, so it could be added to standard library:\n\n```\n    // Checks that the function returns the given error.\n    macro_rules! test_err {\n        ($func:expr, $err:expr) => ({\n            let func = $func;\n\n            match func {\n                Err(ref e) if *e == $err => (),\n                Err(e) => panic!(\"got error {:?}, want {:?}\", e, $err),\n                _ => panic!(\"want error {:?}\", $err),\n            }\n        })\n    }\n```\n", "closed_by": {"login": "steveklabnik", "id": 27786, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI3Nzg2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/27786?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik", "html_url": "https://github.com/steveklabnik", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/34299/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}